item.title: CVE-2020-26814|2024-08-04T16:03:22.683Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20process%20integration%20%28pgp%20-%20module%20business-to-business%20add%20on%29
item.description: SAP Process Integration (PGP Module - Business-to-Business Add On), version - 1.0, allows an attacker to read PGP Keys under certain conditions in the PGP Module of Business-to-Business Add-On, these keys can then be used to read messages processed by the module leading to Information Disclosure.
